Seydou, who was a goat herder before emigrating to America and taking up a career herding cars, quickly made a lasso and chased the animal down. Seydou ultimately grabbed the farm animal by the horns and wouldn’t let go until cops hog-tied the four-legged vagabond into the back of their patrol car.
